Bamboo should have multiple fields for cron expressions - in some cases one cron expression does't do the job

{quote}
Set a scheduled build using the Cron Based Scheduling build strategy for 07:00 Mon-Fri. Also set up 2 other separate build plans to run the same build at 13:00 and 20:00. Is there currently a way to schedule builds to run 07:00, 13:00 and 20:00 Mon-Fri on one build plan instead of creating 3 separate plans?
{quote}

From, [BSP-140|https://support.atlassian.com/browse/BSP-140]

Although, the build is marked as deleted in UI, the build data are not deleted from disk and the embedded HSQL database.

